Description: pdt-client
        ==========
        
        .. image:: https://api.travis-ci.org/paylogic/pdt-client.png
           :target: https://travis-ci.org/paylogic/pdt-client
        
        .. image:: https://pypip.in/v/pdt-client/badge.png
